@startuml Immediate Transfer Flow
title Immediate Transfer Sequence Diagram
participant User as U
participant Frontend as FE
participant Backend as API
participant Supabase as DB
participant Chimoney as CHI

autonumber

== 1. TRANSFER INITIATION ==

U -> FE: Opens "Send Money" screen
activate FE

FE -> API: GET /api/beneficiaries/list\n(X-User-Id: user_uuid)
activate API
API -> DB: SELECT * FROM beneficiaries\nWHERE user_id = ?
activate DB
DB --> API: List of saved beneficiaries
deactivate DB
API --> FE: { beneficiaries: [...] }
deactivate API

FE -> FE: Display beneficiary list\nfor selection

U -> FE: Selects beneficiary (Amit Kumar)
FE -> FE: Shows selected beneficiary details

U -> FE: Enters amount: $500 USD
FE -> FE: Validate amount\n($10 - $50,000)

== 2. GET EXCHANGE RATE ==

FE -> API: GET /api/transfers/exchange-rate?\namount=500&source=USD&target=INR
activate API

API -> CHI: GET /v0.2.4/payouts/rates\n?countryTo=IN
activate CHI
CHI --> API: { rates: { USD: { rate: 83.25 } } }
deactivate CHI

API -> API: Calculate target amount\n500 USD × 83.25 = 41,625 INR\nCalculate fee\n500 × 0.5% = $2.50\nTotal to pay: $502.50

API --> FE: {\n  exchange_rate: 83.25,\n  target_amount: 41625,\n  fee_amount: 2.50,\n  total_to_pay: 502.50\n}
deactivate API

FE -> FE: Display rate breakdown:\n- You send: $502.50\n- Recipient gets: ₹41,625\n- Rate: 1 USD = ₹83.25

== 3. USER CONFIRMS DETAILS ==

U -> FE: Clicks "Confirm & Review"
FE -> FE: Move to review screen\nShow all details with\n"Cannot be reversed" warning

U -> FE: Clicks "Confirm & Send"
FE -> FE: Show loading spinner

== 4. TRANSFER INITIATION (Create Record) ==

FE -> API: POST /api/transfers/initiate\nAuthorization: Bearer token\nX-User-Id: user_uuid\n{\n  beneficiary_id: "abc-123",\n  source_amount: 502.50,\n  source_currency: "USD",\n  exchange_rate: 83.25,\n  fee_amount: 2.50\n}
activate API

API -> API: Validate authorization\nValidate amount, beneficiary

API -> DB: INSERT INTO transfers (\n  user_id, beneficiary_id,\n  source_amount, target_amount,\n  exchange_rate, fee_amount,\n  status: 'pending'\n)
activate DB
DB --> API: transfer_id: "txn-xyz-789"
deactivate DB

API -> DB: INSERT INTO transfer_status_log (\n  transfer_id, old_status: NULL,\n  new_status: 'pending'\n)
deactivate DB

API --> FE: {\n  success: true,\n  transfer_id: "txn-xyz-789",\n  status: "pending"\n}
deactivate API

== 5. TRANSFER EXECUTION (Send to Chimoney) ==

FE -> API: POST /api/transfers/execute\nAuthorization: Bearer token\nX-User-Id: user_uuid\n{\n  transfer_id: "txn-xyz-789"\n}
activate API

API -> DB: BEGIN TRANSACTION
API -> DB: UPDATE transfers\nSET status = 'processing'\nWHERE id = ?
activate DB
DB --> API: OK
deactivate DB

API -> DB: INSERT INTO transfer_status_log (\n  transfer_id, old_status: 'pending',\n  new_status: 'processing'\n)
deactivate DB

note over API: Retrieve beneficiary details\nfrom database

API -> DB: SELECT b.* FROM beneficiaries b\nJOIN transfers t ON b.id = t.beneficiary_id\nWHERE t.id = ?
activate DB
DB --> API: {\n  name: "Amit Kumar",\n  upi_encrypted: "...",\n  account_encrypted: "...",\n  ifsc: "HDFC0000123"\n}
deactivate DB

API -> API: Decrypt sensitive fields\n(AES-256-CBC decryption)

API -> CHI: POST /v0.2.4/payouts/bank\nHeaders: X-API-Key: chimoney_key\n{\n  amount: 500,\n  currency: "USD",\n  account_number: "1234567890",\n  bank_code: "HDFC0000123",\n  fullname: "Amit Kumar",\n  country: "NG",\n  narration: "Payment from Vitta",\n  reference: "TXN_USD_INR_2026_028\"\n}
activate CHI

note over CHI: Chimoney validates account\nProcesses transfer\nReturns transaction ID

CHI --> API: {\n  success: true,\n  data: {\n    id: "chi_9876543210",\n    reference: "TXN_USD_INR_2026_028",\n    status: "pending",\n    received_amount: 41625\n  }\n}
deactivate CHI

API -> DB: UPDATE transfers\nSET\n  status = 'processing',\n  chimoney_transaction_id = 'chi_9876543210',\n  executed_at = NOW()\nWHERE id = ?
activate DB
DB --> API: OK
deactivate DB

API -> DB: INSERT INTO transfer_status_log (\n  transfer_id, old_status: 'processing',\n  new_status: 'processing',\n  metadata: { chimoney_id: '...' }\n)
deactivate DB

API -> DB: COMMIT TRANSACTION
deactivate DB

API --> FE: {\n  success: true,\n  transfer_id: "txn-xyz-789",\n  status: "processing",\n  chimoney_transaction_id: "chi_9876543210",\n  executed_at: "2026-02-28T12:46:00Z",\n  expected_delivery: "2026-02-28T12:51:00Z"\n}
deactivate API

== 6. SHOW CONFIRMATION ==

FE -> FE: Hide loading spinner
FE -> FE: Show confirmation screen with:\n- Transaction ID\n- Recipient: Amit Kumar (UPI)\n- Amount sent: $502.50\n- Amount received: ₹41,625\n- Status: Processing (2-5 min)\n- Time sent: Feb 28, 2026 12:46 PM

U -> FE: Views receipt / Shares / Done

note over DB,CHI: Chimoney processes transfer\nin background (2-5 minutes)\nWill send webhook when completed\n(Future enhancement)

== FUTURE: Webhook Status Update ==

note over CHI: [Optional Future Phase]\nChimoney sends webhook:\nPOST /api/webhooks/chimoney\nwith status: 'completed'

API -> DB: UPDATE transfers\nSET status = 'completed',\ncompletion_at = NOW()\nWHERE chimoney_transaction_id = ?

API -> FE: [Optional] Send push notification\nor email to user:\n"Money received by Amit!"

deactivate FE

@enduml
